Dear Hiring Team,

It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the *Software Engineer* role on the Purchasing Integrations team at *Affirm*. I bring over three years of professional experience building production-grade web applications, APIs, and developer tooling, along with a strong academic foundation as a Master of Science in Computer Science graduate from Pace University, NY.

