My academic experience has sharpened my ability to communicate complex technical decisions clearly and collaborate across disciplines — skills that align directly with the engineering discipline and collaborative culture Affirm's global team values. As an AI Researcher at the Pace Artificial Intelligence Lab, I managed end-to-end model development lifecycles and led workshops on GPU programming and AI agent design for 50+ students, which required breaking down intricate systems into accessible concepts. This same clarity of communication enables me to partner effectively with product management, design, and analytics stakeholders — articulating technical constraints and co-owning trade-off decisions across the product development lifecycle, exactly as this role requires.

I have always been passionate about *putting people first through honest and transparent financial products* and envision myself contributing my talent to the furthering of *Affirm's goal of delivering honest financial products that improve lives by building payment infrastructure grounded in trust*. I would love to discuss my interest in this position with your team and can be reached at #ph or #eml. Thank you for your time and consideration, I look forward to connecting!

